---
<section id="about" class="about band-dark" aria-label="About Wayne Jones">
  <!-- PLACEHOLDER: replace .portrait with Wayne's headshot -->
  <!-- PLACEHOLDER: confirm legal name (Harold Wayne Jones?) -->
  <!-- PLACEHOLDER: confirm AICPA / Georgia Society of CPAs membership -->
  <svg class="band-watermark" viewBox="0 0 600 600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" role="presentation">
    <use href="#guilloche"></use>
  </svg>

  <div class="section-wrap about__grid">
    <div class="about__figure reveal" data-reveal>
      <!-- PLACEHOLDER: when a real headshot <img alt="Wayne Jones, CPA"> is added, remove role="img" + aria-label from .portrait -->
      <figure class="portrait" role="img" aria-label="Wayne Jones, CPA">
        <span class="portrait__corner portrait__corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="portrait__corner portrait__corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="portrait__corner portrait__corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="portrait__corner portrait__corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="portrait__mono">WJ</span>
        <figcaption class="portrait__cap">Wayne Jones, CPA</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <svg class="about__seal" width="104" height="104" viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
        <use href="#wj-seal"></use>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="about__copy reveal" data-reveal style="--d:1">
      <p class="eyebrow eyebrow--gold-ink">Meet your accountant</p>
      <h2 class="section-title section-title--light">A CPA who actually <em>answers the phone.</em></h2>
      <div class="about__columns">
        <p>For more than three decades, Wayne Jones has helped Northwest Georgia businesses and families make sense of their numbers. A Certified Public Accountant licensed in both Georgia and Alabama, Wayne opened Wayne Jones Accounting Services in downtown Rome in 2008 with a simple promise: every client works directly with him — not a rotating cast of associates.</p>
        <p>The result is accounting that's accurate, approachable, and genuinely personal.</p>
      </div>

      <blockquote class="about__quote">
        <span class="about__quote-mark" aria-hidden="true">&ldquo;</span>
        Every client works directly with me.
      </blockquote>

      <dl class="creds-ledger">
        <div class="creds-ledger__row">
          <dt class="creds-ledger__label">Credential</dt>
          <dd class="creds-ledger__value">Certified Public Accountant — GA license #026715</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="creds-ledger__row">
          <dt class="creds-ledger__label">Licensure</dt>
          <dd class="creds-ledger__value">Georgia &amp; Alabama</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="creds-ledger__row">
          <dt class="creds-ledger__label">Experience</dt>
          <dd class="creds-ledger__value">35+ years of accounting practice</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="creds-ledger__row">
          <dt class="creds-ledger__label">Established</dt>
          <dd class="creds-ledger__value">Serving downtown Rome since 2008</dd>
        </div>
        <!-- PLACEHOLDER: add AICPA / Georgia Society of CPAs membership row here once confirmed -->
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
